@baseUrl = http://192.168.43.251:8080

### 获取商品列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### 创建订单
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_method": "wechat",
  "items": [
    {
      "products_id": 22,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "products_id": 22,
      "quantity": 10
    }
  ]
}


### 测试修改后的假逻辑
### =========================================
### 商品模块 (Products) - 软删除测试验证
### =========================================

### 1. 先获取当前所有商品，找一个你想删除的商品 ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### 2. 执行软删除 (假设你要删除 ID 为 1 的商品，请替换为你数据库里真实存在的 ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products?id=25

### 3. 再次获取商品列表，验证该商品是否已经从结果中消失
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### 2. 创建订单 (测试传入不存在的商品ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_method": "alipay",
  "items": [
    {
      "products_id": 9999, 
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}
### 3. 扭转订单状态 (接单制作)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "processing"
}

### 4. 扭转订单状态 (完成订单)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### 5. 扭转订单状态 (测试非法状态)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "hahaha" 
}
### 6. 创建商品 (测试 multipart/form-data)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=极客招牌汉堡&price=28.5&stock=5&is_active=true

#### 7. 获取商品列表，验证新商品是否成功创建
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### 8. 创建订单 (测试正常流程)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_method": "wechat",
  "items": [
    {
      "products_id": 30, 
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

### 9. 创建订单 (测试库存不足)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_method": "alipay",
  "items": [
    {
      "products_id": 30, 
      "quantity": 3
    }
  ]
}

### 8. 老板手动强行上架测试 (无库存状态下)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/30/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_active": true
}